#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
#| msgid "Extraction"
msgid "Extraction planet"
msgstr "Planète d'extraction"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Pull one or two raw P0 resources and refine them on-site into P1 (or "
"straight P2 if you have the feedstock)."
msgstr ""
"Extrayez une ou deux ressources brutes P0 et raffinez-les sur place en P1 "
"(ou directement en P2 si vous avez la matière première)."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "1× Command Center (sets your power/CPU budget — upgrade it fully)."
msgstr ""
"1× Command Center (définit votre budget énergie/CPU — améliorez-le à fond)."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"1× Extractor Control Unit per resource, with as many extractor heads as "
"CPU/PG allows (more heads = more yield, but shorter reach)."
msgstr ""
"1× Extractor Control Unit par ressource, avec autant de têtes d'extracteur "
"que le CPU/PG le permet (plus de têtes = plus de rendement, mais une portée "
"plus courte)."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Basic Industry Facilities to convert P0 → P1 (each does 3,000 P0 → 20 P1 "
"every 30 min)."
msgstr ""
"Des Basic Industry Facilities pour convertir P0 → P1 (chacune fait 3 000 P0 "
"→ 20 P1 toutes les 30 min)."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "1× Launchpad as the export point and buffer storage."
msgstr "1× Launchpad comme point d'export et stockage tampon."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Route extractor output → storage/launchpad → factories → launchpad. Keep the"
" extracted P0 flowing into the BIFs and the finished P1 to the launchpad for"
" export."
msgstr ""
"Routez la production de l'extracteur → stockage/launchpad → usines → "
"launchpad. Faites couler le P0 extrait vers les BIF et le P1 fini vers le "
"launchpad pour l'export."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Export P1 (or P2) via the customs office. Import nothing."
msgstr "Exportez le P1 (ou le P2) via le bureau de douane. N'importez rien."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Import cheaper lower-tier materials and refine them up a tier. No extraction"
" — pure manufacturing throughput."
msgstr ""
"Importez des matériaux de palier inférieur moins chers et raffinez-les d'un "
"palier. Pas d'extraction — du pur débit de fabrication."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "1× Command Center (upgrade fully for CPU/PG)."
msgstr "1× Command Center (améliorez-le à fond pour le CPU/PG)."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "1× Launchpad to receive imports and hold exports."
msgstr "1× Launchpad pour recevoir les imports et stocker les exports."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"As many Advanced Industry Facilities as your power/CPU allows (each does "
"40+40 input → 5 output every hour for P2)."
msgstr ""
"Autant d'Advanced Industry Facilities que votre énergie/CPU le permet "
"(chacune fait 40+40 en entrée → 5 en sortie par heure pour le P2)."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Storage facilities to buffer inputs between imports."
msgstr ""
"Des installations de stockage pour tamponner les intrants entre deux "
"imports."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Import inputs to the launchpad → route to each factory → route finished "
"goods back to the launchpad."
msgstr ""
"Importez les intrants vers le launchpad → routez-les vers chaque usine → "
"routez les biens finis vers le launchpad."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Import the P1/P2 inputs; export the higher-tier product."
msgstr ""
"Importez les intrants P1/P2 ; exportez le produit de palier supérieur."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
#| msgid "Storage / staging"
msgid "Storage / staging planet"
msgstr "Planète de stockage / staging"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"A buffer or consolidation point. Rare for most pilots — usually a launchpad "
"on another planet does the job."
msgstr ""
"Un tampon ou un point de regroupement. Rare pour la plupart des pilotes — en"
" général, un launchpad sur une autre planète suffit."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
#| msgid "Command Center"
msgid "1× Command Center"
msgstr "1× Command Center"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "1× Launchpad"
msgstr "1× Launchpad"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Storage facilities as needed."
msgstr "Des installations de stockage selon les besoins."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Consolidate goods here before a single haul out."
msgstr "Regroupez les marchandises ici avant un unique convoi de sortie."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Export in bulk on your haul day."
msgstr "Exportez en masse le jour de votre convoi."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
#| msgid "Your Command Center"
msgid "Not upgrading the Command Center"
msgstr "Ne pas améliorer le Command Center"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Your Command Center level sets your entire CPU/PG budget. Upgrade it to "
"level 5 before you place facilities, or you'll run out of power halfway "
"through."
msgstr ""
"Le niveau de votre Command Center détermine tout votre budget CPU/PG. "
"Montez-le au niveau 5 avant de placer vos installations, sinon vous tomberez"
" en panne d'énergie à mi-parcours."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Routing errors"
msgstr "Erreurs de routage"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"A facility with no inbound route sits idle; a route to the wrong storage "
"stalls the chain. Follow every product from extractor → factory → launchpad."
msgstr ""
"Une installation sans route entrante reste inactive ; une route vers le "
"mauvais stockage bloque la chaîne. Suivez chaque produit de l'extracteur → "
"l'usine → le launchpad."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
#| msgid "Moon extractions"
msgid "Too many extractor heads"
msgstr "Trop de têtes d'extraction"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"More heads raise yield but shorten the extraction radius and cost CPU/PG. "
"Balance heads against the program length you actually want to run."
msgstr ""
"Plus de têtes augmentent le rendement, mais réduisent le rayon d'extraction "
"et coûtent du CPU/PG. Équilibrez le nombre de têtes avec la durée de "
"programme que vous voulez réellement tenir."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
#| msgid "Insufficient data"
msgid "Insufficient storage"
msgstr "Stockage insuffisant"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"If a launchpad or storage fills up, upstream facilities stop. Size storage "
"for the time between your resets."
msgstr ""
"Si un launchpad ou un stockage sature, les installations en amont "
"s'arrêtent. Dimensionnez le stockage sur l'intervalle entre vos resets."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Wrong schematic"
msgstr "Mauvais schematic"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Setting a factory to the wrong schematic wastes materials. Double-check "
"inputs match what you're actually routing in."
msgstr ""
"Régler une usine sur le mauvais schematic gaspille des matériaux. Vérifiez "
"que les intrants correspondent bien à ce que vous routez vraiment."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
#| msgid "Building facts"
msgid "Overbuilding factories"
msgstr "Construire trop d'usines"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Ten factories starved of feedstock earn less than three that run "
"continuously. Match factory count to your extraction rate."
msgstr ""
"Dix usines à court de matière première rapportent moins que trois qui "
"tournent en continu. Ajustez le nombre d'usines à votre débit d'extraction."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
#| msgid "Customs (POCO) tax"
msgid "Ignoring customs (POCO) tax"
msgstr "Ignorer la taxe de douane (POCO)"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
#| msgid ""
#| "Customs office (POCO) tax on export, as a %. In hostile space this can be "
#| "high — check the POCO before you commit."
msgid ""
"Export/import tax at the customs office is charged on every launch. In "
"hostile space it can dwarf your margin — factor it in before you commit."
msgstr ""
"La taxe d'export/import du bureau de douane est prélevée à chaque lancement."
" En espace hostile, elle peut écraser votre marge — intégrez-la avant de "
"vous engager."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Train Command Center Upgrades to unlock the planet tiers you need."
msgstr ""
"Entraînez Command Center Upgrades pour débloquer les niveaux de planète dont"
" vous avez besoin."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Buy and deploy a Command Center on each planet, then upgrade it fully."
msgstr ""
"Achetez et déployez un Command Center sur chaque planète, puis améliorez-le "
"à fond."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "On extraction planets: place the ECU, add heads, and start a program."
msgstr ""
"Sur les planètes d'extraction : placez l'ECU, ajoutez des têtes et lancez un"
" programme."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Place your factories and set the correct schematic on each."
msgstr "Placez vos usines et réglez le bon schematic sur chacune."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Wire the routes: extractor → storage → factory → launchpad."
msgstr "Câblez les routes : extracteur → stockage → usine → launchpad."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Confirm the customs office tax for your space and your standings."
msgstr ""
"Vérifiez la taxe du bureau de douane pour votre espace et vos réputations."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Set a reset cadence that matches your extractor program length."
msgstr ""
"Fixez une cadence de reset qui correspond à la durée de votre programme "
"d'extraction."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Haul exports to your chosen market hub (or hand to corp buyback)."
msgstr ""
"Convoyez vos exports vers le hub de marché de votre choix (ou remettez-les "
"au buyback de la corp)."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Missing planets"
msgstr "Planètes manquantes"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Not costed"
msgstr "Non chiffré"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Missing prices"
msgstr "Prix manquants"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Unprofitable"
msgstr "Non rentable"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Profitable"
msgstr "Rentable"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "The Planetary Industry planner is currently disabled by leadership."
msgstr ""
"Le planificateur Planetary Industry est actuellement désactivé par la "
"direction."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Add at least one planet — that's what the plan is built around."
msgstr ""
"Ajoutez au moins une planète — c'est autour d'elle que se construit le plan."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Each factory planet needs a product to build — pick one."
msgstr ""
"Chaque planète usine a besoin d'un produit à fabriquer — choisissez-en un."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
#, python-format
msgid "Plan “%(name)s” created — here's your setup and profit estimate."
msgstr ""
"Plan “%(name)s” créé — voici votre configuration et votre estimation de "
"profit."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Plan updated and re-costed."
msgstr "Plan mis à jour et rechiffré."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Keep at least one planet on the plan."
msgstr "Conservez au moins une planète dans le plan."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Re-costed with the latest market prices."
msgstr "Rechiffré avec les derniers prix du marché."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
#, python-format
msgid "Duplicated as “%(name)s”."
msgstr "Dupliqué sous “%(name)s”."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
#, python-format
msgid "Status set to %(status)s."
msgstr "Statut défini sur %(status)s."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
#, python-format
msgid "“%(name)s” archived. Delete again to remove it permanently."
msgstr ""
"“%(name)s” archivé. Supprimez à nouveau pour le retirer définitivement."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
#, python-format
msgid "“%(name)s” permanently deleted."
msgstr "“%(name)s” définitivement supprimé."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
#, python-format
msgid "Colony sync queued for %(count)s pilot(s) — refresh in a minute."
msgstr ""
"Synchronisation des colonies mise en file pour %(count)s pilote(s) — "
"actualisez dans une minute."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Grant the Planetary Industry scope first, then sync your colonies."
msgstr ""
"Accordez d'abord le scope Planetary Industry, puis synchronisez vos "
"colonies."

#: apps/raffle/contest_templates.py
msgid "PVP activity raffle"
msgstr "Tombola d'activité PVP"

#: apps/raffle/contest_templates.py
msgid ""
"Reward everyone who undocks and gets on kills. Solo 100 · final blow 10 · "
"participation 1."
msgstr ""
"Récompensez tous ceux qui sortent du dock et participent aux kills. Solo 100"
" · coup de grâce 10 · participation 1."

#: apps/raffle/contest_templates.py
#| msgid "Solo kills"
msgid "Solo kill challenge"
msgstr "Défi kills solo"

#: apps/raffle/contest_templates.py
msgid ""
"Heavily reward solo PvP prowess — solo kills are worth 10× a normal kill."
msgstr ""
"Récompensez fortement les exploits en PvP solo — un kill solo vaut 10× un "
"kill normal."

#: apps/raffle/contest_templates.py
#| msgid "Home defence"
msgid "Home defence contest"
msgstr "Concours de défense du territoire"

#: apps/raffle/contest_templates.py
msgid ""
"Reward kills defending home space. Set the home region/systems in the PVP "
"filters."
msgstr ""
"Récompensez les kills réalisés en défense de votre espace. Définissez la "
"région / les systèmes du territoire dans les filtres PVP."

#: apps/raffle/contest_templates.py
#| msgid "Mining tax"
msgid "Mining month"
msgstr "Mois du minage"

#: apps/raffle/contest_templates.py
msgid "Reward ore mined from the corp mining ledger (X tickets per m³)."
msgstr ""
"Récompensez le minerai extrait, d'après le registre de minage de la corp (X "
"tickets par m³)."

#: apps/raffle/contest_templates.py
#| msgid "In production"
msgid "Industry production drive"
msgstr "Campagne de production industrielle"

#: apps/raffle/contest_templates.py
msgid ""
"Recognise builders. Industry has no reliable per-pilot feed, so awards are "
"officer-approved."
msgstr ""
"Mettez les producteurs à l'honneur. L'industrie n'a pas de flux fiable par "
"pilote : les attributions sont donc validées par un officier."

#: apps/raffle/contest_templates.py
#| msgid "No such campaign."
msgid "Logistics support campaign"
msgstr "Campagne de soutien logistique"

#: apps/raffle/contest_templates.py
msgid "Reward haulers for delivered courier contracts (officer-approved)."
msgstr ""
"Récompensez les transporteurs pour les contrats de courrier livrés (validé "
"par un officier)."

#: apps/raffle/contest_templates.py
#| msgid "No past contests yet"
msgid "Newbro support contest"
msgstr "Concours de soutien aux newbros"

#: apps/raffle/contest_templates.py
msgid ""
