#: templates/industry/guide.html
msgid "Blueprints: BPO vs BPC"
msgstr "Blueprints : BPO vs BPC"

#: templates/industry/guide.html
msgid ""
"A <strong>blueprint</strong> is the recipe for building something. There are"
" two kinds:"
msgstr ""
"Un <strong>blueprint</strong> est la recette pour fabriquer quelque chose. "
"Il en existe deux types :"

#: templates/industry/guide.html
msgid ""
"<strong class=\"text-ink\">BPO — Blueprint Original.</strong> Reusable "
"forever. You buy it once (from CCP-seeded market orders for T1) and can "
"build from it endlessly, and <em>research</em> it to make it more efficient."
msgstr ""
"<strong class=\"text-ink\">BPO — Blueprint Original.</strong> Réutilisable "
"pour toujours. Vous l'achetez une fois (via des ordres de marché fournis par"
" CCP pour le T1) et pouvez fabriquer à l'infini, et le <em>rechercher</em> "
"pour le rendre plus efficace."

#: templates/industry/guide.html
msgid ""
"<strong class=\"text-ink\">BPC — Blueprint Copy.</strong> A copy with a "
"limited number of runs. Made by <em>copying</em> a BPO, or produced by "
"<em>invention</em> (that's how you get T2/T3 blueprints — there are no T2 "
"BPOs)."
msgstr ""
"<strong class=\"text-ink\">BPC — Blueprint Copy.</strong> Une copie avec un "
"nombre de cycles limité. Créée en <em>copiant</em> un BPO, ou produite par "
"<em>invention</em> (c'est ainsi qu'on obtient les blueprints T2/T3 — il "
"n'existe pas de BPO T2)."

#: templates/industry/guide.html
msgid "Manufacturing, ME and TE"
msgstr "Fabrication, ME et TE"

#: templates/industry/guide.html
msgid ""
"<strong>Manufacturing</strong> turns materials into the product using a "
"blueprint, in an industry job that takes time and costs a job fee. Two "
"blueprint attributes matter:"
msgstr ""
"La <strong>fabrication</strong> transforme des matériaux en produit à l'aide"
" d'un blueprint, dans un job d'industrie qui prend du temps et coûte des "
"frais de job. Deux attributs de blueprint comptent :"

#: templates/industry/guide.html
#, python-format
msgid ""
"<strong class=\"text-ink\">ME — Material Efficiency (0–10).</strong> Each "
"level cuts the materials a job consumes by 1%%, up to 10%% at ME 10. Higher "
"ME = cheaper builds. Research it on a BPO before mass production."
msgstr ""
"<strong class=\"text-ink\">ME — Material Efficiency (0–10).</strong> Chaque "
"niveau réduit de 1%% les matériaux consommés par un job, jusqu'à 10%% au ME "
"10. Un ME plus élevé = des fabrications moins chères. Recherchez-le sur un "
"BPO avant la production de masse."

#: templates/industry/guide.html
#, python-format
msgid ""
"<strong class=\"text-ink\">TE — Time Efficiency (0–20).</strong> Each level "
"cuts the job <em>time</em> by 1%%, up to 20%%. It doesn't change materials "
"or cost, only how long the job runs."
msgstr ""
"<strong class=\"text-ink\">TE — Time Efficiency (0–20).</strong> Chaque "
"niveau réduit le <em>temps</em> du job de 1%%, jusqu'à 20%%. Cela ne change "
"ni les matériaux ni le coût, seulement la durée du job."

#: templates/industry/guide.html
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The <a href=\"%(calc_url)s\" class=\"text-cyan "
"hover:underline\">Manufacturing calculator</a> applies ME for you and shows "
"the material bill after efficiency."
msgstr ""
"Le <a href=\"%(calc_url)s\" class=\"text-cyan hover:underline\">calculateur "
"de fabrication</a> applique le ME pour vous et affiche la nomenclature des "
"matériaux après efficacité."

#: templates/industry/guide.html
msgid "Copying and research"
msgstr "Copie et recherche"

#: templates/industry/guide.html
msgid "Three more blueprint jobs, all run on a BPO:"
msgstr "Trois autres jobs de blueprint, tous exécutés sur un BPO :"

#: templates/industry/guide.html
msgid ""
"<strong class=\"text-ink\">Copying</strong> makes BPCs from a BPO (needed as"
" the input to invention)."
msgstr ""
"La <strong class=\"text-ink\">copie</strong> crée des BPC à partir d'un BPO "
"(nécessaires comme intrant à l'invention)."

#: templates/industry/guide.html
msgid ""
"<strong class=\"text-ink\">ME research</strong> raises Material Efficiency; "
"<strong class=\"text-ink\">TE research</strong> raises Time Efficiency."
msgstr ""
"La <strong class=\"text-ink\">recherche ME</strong> augmente la Material "
"Efficiency ; la <strong class=\"text-ink\">recherche TE</strong> augmente la"
" Time Efficiency."

#: templates/industry/guide.html
msgid "T2 invention"
msgstr "Invention T2"

#: templates/industry/guide.html
msgid ""
"<strong>Invention</strong> is how you make Tech II. You take a <strong>T1 "
"BPC</strong>, add <strong>datacores</strong> (and optionally a "
"<strong>decryptor</strong>), and run an invention job that <em>might</em> "
"succeed. On success you get a T2 BPC with a few runs."
msgstr ""
"L'<strong>invention</strong> est la façon de fabriquer du Tech II. Vous "
"prenez un <strong>BPC T1</strong>, ajoutez des <strong>datacores</strong> "
"(et éventuellement un <strong>decryptor</strong>), et lancez un job "
"d'invention qui <em>peut</em> réussir. En cas de succès, vous obtenez un BPC"
" T2 avec quelques cycles."

#: templates/industry/guide.html
msgid ""
"<strong class=\"text-ink\">Datacores</strong> — consumable science items, "
"spent whether the job succeeds or fails."
msgstr ""
"<strong class=\"text-ink\">Datacores</strong> — objets scientifiques "
"consommables, dépensés que le job réussisse ou échoue."

#: templates/industry/guide.html
msgid ""
"<strong class=\"text-ink\">Decryptor</strong> — an optional modifier that "
"trades success chance for more runs / better ME / TE on the resulting BPC."
msgstr ""
"<strong class=\"text-ink\">Decryptor</strong> — un modificateur optionnel "
"qui échange des chances de succès contre plus de cycles / un meilleur ME / "
"TE sur le BPC obtenu."

#: templates/industry/guide.html
#, python-format
msgid ""
"<strong class=\"text-ink\">Probability</strong> — the chance a single job "
"succeeds. It rises with your science + encryption skills and the decryptor. "
"If a job has a 34%% chance, you'll average about 3 attempts per success — so"
" the <em>real</em> cost per T2 BPC includes the datacores you burned on the "
"failures."
msgstr ""
"<strong class=\"text-ink\">Probabilité</strong> — la chance qu'un seul job "
"réussisse. Elle augmente avec vos compétences de science et d'encryption et "
"le decryptor. Si un job a 34%% de chances, il vous faudra en moyenne environ"
" 3 tentatives par succès — le coût <em>réel</em> par BPC T2 inclut donc les "
"datacores gaspillés sur les échecs."

#: templates/industry/guide.html
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The <a href=\"%(inv_url)s\" class=\"text-cyan hover:underline\">T2 invention"
" planner</a> does this maths — probability, expected attempts, and cost per "
"successful BPC — and tells you whether it's cheaper to invent, buy the BPC, "
"or just buy the finished T2 item."
msgstr ""
